Tech Quotes Inspirational

1. “Technology is best when it brings people together.”

2. “The Web as I envisaged it, we have not seen it yet. The future is still so much bigger than the past.”

3. “If future generations are to remember us more with gratitude than sorrow, we must achieve more than just the miracles of technology. We must also leave them a glimpse of the world as it was created, not just as it looked when we got through with it.”

4. “It's not a faith in technology. It's faith in people.”

5. “The advance of technology is based on making it fit in so that you don't really even notice it, so it's part of everyday life.”

6. “Technology is a useful servant but a dangerous master.”
